            <p>
              We're excited to launch the Open Call for Applications for the <strong>Digital Democracy Hackathon</strong>!
              <br><br>
              <a href="https://metamorphosis.org.mk/" target="_blank">Metamorphosis Foundation</a> and the <a href="https://civicliteraci.es/" target="_blank">Civic Literacy Initiative</a> are partnering with <a href="https://www.civicus.org/" target="_blank">CIVICUS</a> to host this hackathon in our region, joining a global series of hackathons organized as part of the <a href="https://digitaldemocracyinitiative.net/" target="_blank">Digital Democracy Initiative (DDI)</a>, a worldwide effort to support civil society in strengthening civic space and promoting inclusive democracy.
            </p>
          </TabsPanel>
